2007-10-19  John J. Foerch  <jjfoerch@earthlink.net>

	* components/commandline.js (handle): new variable suppress_rc.
	Eval switch, `-i', changed to `-e'.  Eval switch no longer
	automatically suppresses opening a window.  Batch mode switch `-q'
	changed to `-batch'.  New switch `-l'.  New switch `-q' to
	suppress rc.  Conditionally load rc.

	* components/application.js (get_chrome_contents): use dump
	instead of dumpln.

	* components/application.js (application.set_default_directory):
	new function, and accompanying variable, `default_directory'.

	* components/application.js (application): load debug.js and
	localfile.js.

	* components/application.js (application.encode_xpcom_structure)
	(application.decode_xpcom_structure, application.add_hook)
	(application.generate_new_frame_tag)
	(application.get_frame_by_tag): new.

	* components/application.js (application.run_hooks): rewrote.  new
	parameter, `scope'.

	* components/application.js (application.generate_new_frame_name)
	(application.get_frame_by_name): removed.

	* components/application.js (application.make_frame): replaced
	`name' with `tag'.  new way of encoding arguments to pass to the
	frame.  run make_frame_hook.

